According to the order of the Chief Sanitary Doctor of the Almaty Region № 10 dated on 11th May 2020, starting from 11th May 2020, Akims of districts and cities, the Regional Health Department are required to ensure that:

- persons working on a rotational basis, demobilized from the facilities of Tengizchevroil LLP at the place of arrival, are subject to isolation in a quarantine hospital for laboratory examination for COVID-19 for up to 2 days;
- persons with a positive result are transferred to an infectious diseases hospital for treatment;
- persons with a negative result on COVID-19 are isolated at home (home quarantine) for 12 days. In the absence of conditions for isolation at home, isolation in a quarantine hospital is recommended.

