By the order of the Chief Sanitary Doctor of the Almaty Region № 6 dated on 13th April 2020, subjects (objects) of entrepreneurship in the field of public catering are required to:

1) carry out activities only by delivering goods (food, drinks, etc.) to the consumer in a disposable package;
2) ensure the use of disposable gloves and masks by personnel during work (change of masks at least once every 3 hours);
3) do not allow personnel with manifestations of acute respiratory infections (fever, cough, runny nose, etc.) to work;
4) install hand sanitizers at the inlet and outlet;
5) carry out airing and wet cleaning of premises using disinfectants for door handles, handrails, tables, chair backs, escalator handrails, stairs, doors, floors;
6) carry out enhanced disinfection cleaning of toilets, including outbuildings, every 3 hours of work and at the end of the work shift.

